  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Companion Appearance Enhancement</span>. This dual-purpose laser responds to the biological vitals of its wearer, providing an adaptive level of warmth and light, as well as soft pulses to soothe anxiety.<br><br>Earn the trust of wild animals to adopt companions. Interact with companions to customise their appearance.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">同伴外观强化</span>。这种两用激光能对佩戴者的重要生物指标做出响应，提供相应的热量和光照，以及舒缓焦虑的软脉冲。<br><br>赢得野生动物的信任来收养同伴。与同伴互动来自定义它们的外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特<span class=\"name name-stellar\">同伴外觀強化</span>。此雙功能雷射會針對穿戴者的生命跡象，提供適當的溫熱與光，並發出柔和的波動，舒緩穿戴者的緊張。<br><br>獲得野生動物的信任，即可收養為同伴。與同伴互動，自訂其外觀。"
  },
